This guide explains how to request correctly a stabilization of a package present in the Gentoo main tree.

== Prerequisites ==
If you want to request a stabilization, you need to have an account on the Gentoo Bugzilla. After successfully logged in, you can search if the stabilization of the package has already been requested. You can't request a stabilization for packages that are not present in the Gentoo main tree (e.g. overlays).

